title: CHAPTER 01 Mortal Kombat History
description:
**BASED ON THE GAME STORY + TOTALLY WACKED PRODUCTIONS (2010) MORTAL KOMBAT STORY**

Welcome to the UNLEASHED UNIVERSE (MORTAL KOMBAT edition) seasons 1,2+3
We see how the galaxy has been affected by Mortal Kombat in the past, and the devastastion in it's wake, we get a first hand veiw of the 9th tournament on Earth, and even the final match of tournament 9 with Kung Lao Vs Shang Tsung. 

**OLD SCHOOL MARTIAL ART FANS WILL ENJOY A BONUS THEY NEVER SAW COMING** - and fans of the game series should enjoy the level of story accuracy. 

**featuring the 1997 series, the 95' and 97' movies - all the way through to Mortal Kombat Legacy, and then on to the apolocolyptic events of MK9 (2011) the Outworld Apocolypse of Earth**

over 100 episodes ready,  and more coming soon!


Please enjoy, thank you for watching, this story gets better as it progress' - 
so please be patient with it, I promise in time ..... - "it will be great"

Miss_Kitti of JazzyRock Pictures Australia
